      "name": "List 7",
      "chunk_text": "Baseline script policy for the HTML Viewer. Effective per-page behavior remains auto by default: shared rich-media + iframe heuristics decide when scripts are needed for DOM export versus when they should be stripped. Most work should leave this at its safe default.",
