      ],
      "name": "FloatingPanel Chat injects a strict Markdown response contract system prompt; st",
      "chunk_text": "FloatingPanel Chat injects a strict Markdown response contract system prompt; standard chat responses may include one `response:` YAML metadata block when non-trivial, while `chatKnowgrph` persists only the structured KGC contract. The Chat UI shows one final assistant message: concise bullets (≤50 words) plus a workspace link to the current `kgc_yyyymmddhhmmss.md`.",
      "properties": {
        "text": "FloatingPanel Chat injects a strict Markdown response contract system prompt; standard chat responses may include one `response:` YAML metadata block when non-trivial, while `chatKnowgrph` persists only the structured KGC contract. The Chat UI shows one final assistant message: concise bullets (≤50 words) plus a workspace link to the current `kgc_yyyymmddhhmmss.md`.",
        "ordered": false,
        "index": null,
        "order": 9
      },
      "metadata": {
