      "chunk_text": "`chatHistoryWorkspacePath` optionally pins a workspace Markdown file path to append chat exchanges; when empty, the first successful chat will create `chh_yyyymmddhhmmss.md` under `chatLocalStorageRootPath` and continue appending there so the history is viewable and editable in the Workspace Editor.",
